- next@14.2.3
- react, react-dom
- @supabase/supabase-js@^2.43.4
- @supabase/ssr@^0.3.0
- zod@^3.23.8
- tailwindcss, postcss, autoprefixer

폰트: Noto Sans KR (Google Fonts)
컬러: brand.red = #A50034 (tailwind.config에 추가)

디렉토리 구조:
